I"j<h1 id="voron-switchwire---skr-mini-e3-v20-wiring">Voron Switchwire - SKR mini E3 V2.0 Wiring</h1>

<h2 id="mcu">MCU</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Plug in stepper motors for X, Y, Z, and E in positions Xm, Ym, ZAm, and Em</li>
  <li>Plug Hot End thermistor to thermistor TH0</li>
  <li>Plug Hot End heater in to E0</li>
  <li>Plug Hot End Fan in to FAN1</li>
  <li>Plug Part Cooling Fan in to FAN0</li>
  <li>Plug Bed Thermistor in to THB</li>
  <li>Connect Bed Heater to HB connector</li>
  <li>Connect X end stop to X-STOP connector</li>
  <li>Connect Y end stop to Y-STOP connector</li>
  <li>Plug Probe GND and Signal (with BAT85 diode) in to Z-STOP</li>
  <li>Connect Probe +V to VIN in terminal next to HB</li>
  <li>Wire 24V and -V from DC power supply to VIN and GND terminals in corner</li>
  <li>Connect USB Cable to your SKR mini E3, but do not connect it yet to your Raspberry Pi</li>
</ul>

